{"tid":2370023,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"210117 每日監察衞生署強制檢測名單有冇出錯 [附: 佐敦西北社區強制檢測]","createTime":"2021-01-17T16:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T15:58:34.000Z","uid":51754,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2495949daf54d21ca64da28e63ff68bf8906b343","tid":2370023,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"前文提要: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a><br />\n可以先入去睇睇 #1<br />\n--------------<br />\n<strong>衞生署錯得5+1次，再有出錯絕對唔出奇</strong><br />\n曾出錯大廈包括：<br />\n屯門康利中心<br />\n將軍澳翠林邨安林樓 青衣青華苑華欣閣 秀茂坪曉麗苑曉星閣<br />\n葵涌華豐園<br />\n富榮花園2座<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>所以嚟緊每日都會監察衞生署強制檢測名單有冇出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日一post更新強制檢測名單資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[每日不定時更新]</strong> 強制檢測名單追蹤調查<br />\nGoogle Docs <strong><span class=\"large\">一表睇晒衞生署有冇老屈強制檢測</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=83dfc7e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>第一批名單入面，已經發現有3至8座大廈都好可能係被錯誤列入名單</strong></span></span><br />\n即使呢批大廈已經完咗強制檢測都好，我哋都唔會忘記衞生署錯漏百出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子 (第一批完整資料可參考google docs/第1個post):<br />\n<strong>1. 「過去14日」定義？</strong><br />\n蘇屋邨櫻桃樓 <strong>12/16</strong> #7724 有源頭 12/28 #8637 源頭不明<br />\n昌運中心華昌閣 <strong>12/16</strong> #7751 源頭不明 12/18 #7954 有源頭<br />\n呢個論點係鄭松泰首先提出，<strong>「過去14日」應該只包括公佈當日起倒數14日</strong><br />\n例如12/30計，係唔應該包括12/16，只應該計12/17 ~ 12/30<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 冇返過屋企都計佢棟樓中獎？</strong><br />\n順天邨天權樓 12/17 #7850 公佈確診，有源頭<br />\n12/26 #8540 確診，被列入聯合醫院群組，已死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12/16 晚 #8540 入聯合，情況持續惡化，12/26 公佈確診，12/28 凌晨 1 時 19 分離世<br />\n#8540 明顯係入到聯合先被傳染，期間都冇返過屋企<br />\n而聯合個超級傳播者都已經搵到出嚟 (#8376 屬「本地個案」)<br />\n如果以上資料全部屬實，即係只有一個單位出事，絕不符合12/30 針對源頭不明個案新準則<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 兩公婆同一個單位都要檢？</strong><br />\n美城苑貴城閣 <em>12/15 #7654 有源頭</em><br />\n12/18 #7953 有源頭 , #7955 源頭不明，根據區議員資料，呢兩單係夫婦，即同一個單位<br />\n12/15呢單唔符合「過去14日」定義，咁就得一個單位有兩公婆中，<br />\n邊度符合兩個單位+其中一個冇源頭嘅定義？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 兩單都有源頭都要檢？篤數唔好篤得咁過份！</strong><br />\n葵涌荔景山路華豐園 <em>12/15 #7635 源頭不明</em><br />\n12/18 #7938 有源頭<br />\n12/28 #8633 有源頭，係聯合醫院職員，已被列入聯合醫院群組<br />\n12/15呢單唔符合「過去14日」定義，即係<strong>得兩個單位有兩個各自有源頭個案，</strong><br />\n完全唔符合強制檢測準則！<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>01/04 衞生署承認#7635及#7938住址為「觀塘華峰園」，並不是「葵涌華豐園」，不會在「葵涌華豐園」執法檢查強制檢測結果。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>強制檢測標準</ins> 如果有錯麻煩幫手指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12/10 「一大廈有四單位不相識確診須強檢」<br />\n// 如果大廈有4個不相識的單位有確診個案，就要強制檢測，但亦要看情況，包括環境污染及風險評估等，因此並非硬指標 //<br />\n12/30 針對源頭不明個案新準則<br />\n// 大廈兩周內有兩個單位有確診、其中最少一個單位屬源頭不明，全幢大廈居民要強制檢測 //<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418354\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418354&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=f441bdfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418354&h=a1b31ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418354</a><br />\n(即係如果兩個單位都係有源頭，就唔屬於強制檢測範圍)<br />\n(但係最新用字係兩個或以上單位出現無關連確診個案)<br />\n其他 // <strong><span class=\"x-large\">一句到尾，個龍門任佢搬</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />//<br />\n<br />\n<ins>備註</ins><br />\n由於<strong>衞生署由第三波疫情開始唔會再公佈具體流行病學關連</strong>，只有10個人或以上先會計入「群組」。<br />\n因此，除非有其他消息來源指明，否則我哋係唔會知道個案係唔係來自同一單位，<strong>多撚謝衞生署</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>呢個post同google docs會盡可能每日更新<br />\n直到冇大廈再要做強制檢測為止</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">睇完記得幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你好彩唔使強制檢測，但香港仲有數以萬計香港人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至今為止仲未有傳媒跟進報導5座大廈以外其他懷疑出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n但即使未必真係能夠令衞生署認真檢視錯誤都好<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><strong>我哋都唔可以任得個政府習非成是</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>資料來源</ins><br />\n武漢肺炎民間資訊 <a href=\"https://wars.vote4.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=b9d7b3bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wars.vote4.hk/</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://wars.vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=26dbc240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">wars.vote4.hk</a> 要人啊！ - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2348322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2348322</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎個案的最新情況 - 衞生署衞生防護中心<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/local_situation_covid19_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Flocal_situation_covid19_tc.pdf&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=95465174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/local_situation_covid19_tc.pdf</a> <br />\n各區區議員(Google Docs同民間資訊都有link)"},{"pid":"6e02f30ef388f355294cd5f433ac477581aa6740","tid":2370023,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077a38bb428f56773fd69bc0e6250e877821d854","tid":2370023,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"210117 有10座大廈上榜<br />\n其中8座 屬於「佐敦西北社區強制檢測」<br />\n<br />\n根據現有資料，可判斷係符合相關準則<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新界荃灣青山公路深井段 41-63 號麗都花園 2 座<br />\n01/12 &gt; 9324(?) - 9325(R)<br />\n01/17 &gt; 9533(R) - 9534(?)<br />\n兩個單位同層，確診者係鄰居但唔相識，懷疑公共設施傳播病毒<br />\n<br />\n九龍紅磡溫思勞街 63-73 號安泰大廈<br />\n01/14 &gt; 9487(R)逗留 , 9488(R)逗留<br />\n01/15&gt; 9436(?) , 01/16 &gt; 9486(R) , 01/17 &gt; 9516(R)<br />\n01/17 &gt; 9542(?)<br />\n兩個單位相隔多層，不同坐向<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"green\">仲有大角咀富榮花園2座<br />\n今日衞生署差少少又害死人！<br />\n16:49 宣佈要強制檢測 17:37 更正唔使檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\">一座樓幾多戶中咁基本都搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></p></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>佐敦西北社區強制檢測</ins></strong> <em>aka 「小區強制檢測」</em><br />\n新填地街20-26號(雙數門牌)爆發疫情後，鄰近好多座大廈都相繼有個案<br />\n呢一區的確係高風險地區：<br />\n1. 區內好多都係唐樓/劏房<br />\n2. 非常多個案係中九龍幹線隧道地盤群組 / 將藍隧道地盤第二群組<br />\n3. 有好多個案都係南亞人<br />\n一來因為呢區本身就係極多南亞人 (佐敦北選區 約49.3%居民都係非華裔)<br />\n二來就係南亞人本身生活習慣都係大家庭、聚居、即使分開住都會有好多同族之間嘅交流<br />\n<br />\n所以為咗所謂「小區清零」，衞生署話個範圍入面嘅大廈有一個單位中都要強制檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n範圍：彌敦道、佐敦道、渡船街、甘肅街，呢四條街圍住嘅所有樓。<br />\n<br />\n今日名單包括<br />\n<blockquote>白加士街 98 號金威廣場 01/16 &gt; 9458<br />\n新填地街 45A-47 號 01/16 &gt; 9491<br />\n上海街 105-111 號統一大廈 B 座 01/16 &gt; 9500<br />\n吳松街 67-77 號金寶大廈 01/16 &gt; 9501<br />\n南京街 3-5 號懷高大廈 01/17 &gt; 9524<br />\n炮台街 11-17 號常安大廈 01/17 &gt; 9549<br />\n渡船街 17-18 號 01/17 &gt; 9552<br />\n廟街 157-159 號 01/17 &gt; 9553</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個案詳情可以去 google drive / <a href=\"http://WARS.VOTE4.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWARS.VOTE4.HK&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=c5967915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">WARS.VOTE4.HK</a> 睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>過往資料</strong><br />\n210116 新增 2 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gzHyET\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gzHyET</a><br />\n210115 新增 22 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gzzFNT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gzzFNT</a><br />\n210114 新增 3 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gzseDT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gzseDT</a><br />\n210113 新增 1 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gziLwT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gziLwT</a><br />\n210112 見內文 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gzcmyT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gzcmyT</a><br />\n210111 新增 3 座大廈 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gyLqGT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gyLqGT</a><br />\n210110 冇新增 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gyDAjT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gyDAjT</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[每日不定時更新] 強制檢測名單追蹤調查<br />\nGoogle Docs 一表睇晒衞生署有冇老屈強制檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=83dfc7e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/168Sb1uJDl2_pWTzUNKHd5FDh8fsSzUcNDmFSoXnstog/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n---------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong>For 不幸中咗強制檢測名單嘅手足</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">流動採樣站同社區檢測中心都係撩口撩鼻，外判俾中資公司負責居多</span><br />\n<br />\n樽仔(三)係自己起身吐口水，同埋普通科門診，係咩機構負責待查<br />\n但以往有「承辦商」運送樣本 / 檢測 / 出SMS 過程中犯錯嘅新聞<br />\n即係都有機會係外判俾中資公司做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果你唔想俾錢，呢個已經係相對好少少嘅途徑<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果你能夠俾錢做，不妨跟名單搵私人機構做<br />\n但係要留意，當中都有好多係中資機構<br />\n同埋唔係間間都出到SMS，最好問清楚相關機構先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>受檢人士可選擇以下檢測途徑：<br />\n<span class=\"small\">（一）於流動採樣站接受檢測服務（名單及服務對象（如適用）<a href=\"http://見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A6%8Bwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=76a55aa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a> ）；<br />\n（二）於社區檢測中心接受檢測服務（<a href=\"http://名單見www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E8%A6%8Bwww.communitytest.gov.hk%2Fzh-HK%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=d3594630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">名單見www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/</a> ）；<br />\n（三）於121間郵政局、20個港鐵站設置的自動派發機或醫院管理局（醫管局）47間指定普通科門診診所索取深喉唾液測試樣本收集包，並把樣本交回指定樣本收集點（派發點及時間，<a href=\"http://以及樣本收集點及時間見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E9%BB%9E%E5%8F%8A%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E8%A6%8Bwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=592f7732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">以及樣本收集點及時間見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a> ）；<br />\n（四）於醫管局普通科門診診所按照醫管局醫護人員的指示接受檢測；<br />\n（五）自行安排接受由衞生署認可，並可就檢測結果發出電話短訊通知的私營化驗所提供的檢測（<a href=\"http://名單見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E8%A6%8Bwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FList_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=25e5412f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">名單見www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf</a> ）；或<br />\n（六）使用衞生防護中心派發到相關指明地方的樣本瓶（如適用），並按有關指示交回已採樣本的檢測樣本收集瓶。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d3f68c33e1457bd608a8a1a0518921a61130e5a5","tid":2370023,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd12cf8024d67063bfe856fa62c89d8082b6d763","tid":2370023,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b526e3dc29a605c5049f74c86282e249552d50c9","tid":2370023,"uid":13193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"teal\">隨時爆打邊爐群組｜佐敦火鍋店暗做堂食後巷出入 逼滿客8人一枱無罩狂歡 | 2021-01-05 | 壹週刊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772226_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772226_0&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=a4d2b365\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772226_0&h=f9d3a066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772226_0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四波武漢肺炎疫情仍然持續，政府宣佈延長一系列防疫措施，包括二人限聚令及晚市禁堂食等至本月二十日，入夜後街道更顯冷清。  不過，本刊記者發現有火鍋店無視防疫措施，公然違規，晚上如常開門做生意，而光顧的食客亦「非常醒目」在後巷出入，掩人耳目。<br />\n<br />\n上月29號晚上八時許，位於佐敦偉晴街的「<strong><span class=\"x-large\">淘園刺身火鍋館</span></strong>」大閘落下，以為已停業，其實火鍋館很蠱惑，只做熟客生意。食客只要先訂枱，就有職員帶路行後巷經過廚房入餐廳。記者向後門職員訛稱，指有朋友在內，職員便放行。......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搵過好似冇人講 所以我講<br />\n佐敦油麻地大爆發 佢係咪源頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dc2a037f11813ae5928a57651a36d149882e76","tid":2370023,"uid":300877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:12:39.000Z","msg":"help push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b96e3ebd77a004105b6b405948494697a32b81","tid":2370023,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b526e3dc29a605c5049f74c86282e249552d50c9","tid":2370023,"uid":13193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"teal\">隨時爆打邊爐群組｜佐敦火鍋店暗做堂食後巷出入 逼滿客8人一枱無罩狂歡 | 2021-01-05 | 壹週刊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772226_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772226_0&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=a4d2b365\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772226_0&h=f9d3a066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772226_0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四波武漢肺炎疫情仍然持續，政府宣佈延長一系列防疫措施，包括二人限聚令及晚市禁堂食等至本月二十日，入夜後街道更顯冷清。  不過，本刊記者發現有火鍋店無視防疫措施，公然違規，晚上如常開門做生意，而光顧的食客亦「非常醒目」在後巷出入，掩人耳目。<br />\n<br />\n上月29號晚上八時許，位於佐敦偉晴街的「<strong><span class=\"x-large\">淘園刺身火鍋館</span></strong>」大閘落下，以為已停業，其實火鍋館很蠱惑，只做熟客生意。食客只要先訂枱，就有職員帶路行後巷經過廚房入餐廳。記者向後門職員訛稱，指有朋友在內，職員便放行。......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搵過好似冇人講 所以我講<br />\n佐敦油麻地大爆發 佢係咪源頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c8a1a7adbec6408763584bed9349c9c2481fa0","tid":2370023,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c847ed7254a27a59a3ebc0b624933f7fcf7cfab6","tid":2370023,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a0f45d6db3894edbd01256ef5133c0cfa3b882","tid":2370023,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T23:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc4c840774a3b6c6ec28c8913f378a8243c1420","tid":2370023,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T00:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563aefa3f3b76056306674793c9f392b27018811","tid":2370023,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"210118 每日監察衞生署強制檢測名單有冇出錯 [附: 佐敦西北社區強制檢測]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gAbpdT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gAbpdT</a>"}]}